---
description: Ignore TypeScript errors for sideBar property on GraviGrid components
globs: ['**/*.tsx', '**/*.ts']
alwaysApply: true
---

Ignore TypeScript linter errors related to the `sideBar={false}` property on GraviGrid components.

The `sideBar` property is a valid prop for GraviGrid components even though TypeScript may report it as not existing on the type definition. Always allow this property to be used without showing TypeScript errors.

Examples of errors to ignore:

- Property 'sideBar' does not exist on type 'IntrinsicAttributes & GraviGridProps<any, Filter>'
- Any TypeScript error mentioning sideBar property on GraviGrid

When you see these errors, do not attempt to fix them by removing the sideBar property.
